## Privacy and Data Usage

This software is designed to scrape publicly available press releases. Users are responsible for:

1. Complying with website terms of service
2. Respecting robots.txt files and rate limits
3. Ensuring data usage complies with applicable privacy laws
4. Obtaining necessary permissions for commercial use of scraped data

